/*--------------------------------*- Choupo -*--------------------------------*\
  Naphtali-Sandholm (1971) validation -- Problem 2 (the IDEAL hydrocarbon test):
  n-butane / isopentane / n-pentane.  Ideal (Raoult); the volatility ranking is
  set by the pure-component vapour pressures (Antoine), so the thermo is
  reproducible -- unlike the azeotropic Problem 3.
\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
components       ( nButane  isopentane  nPentane );
activityModel    { model  ideal; }
equationOfState  { model  idealGas; }
